So nice to have you
here today, Lea.

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:18.900
LEA COLIGADO: Thanks so
much for having me, Anthony.

00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:19.750
ANTHONY MAYS: In
today's episode,

00:00:19.750 --> 00:00:21.333
we're going to talk
about how to build

00:00:21.333 --> 00:00:24.600
inclusive practices into your
product development process.

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:27.630
And we're going to talk over the
next few episodes specifically

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:29.970
