00:00:39.044 --> 00:00:41.460
So Lea, it's so great to have
you here to talk about this,

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:43.740
and to share your knowledge
and expertise with us today.

00:00:43.740 --> 00:00:45.781
If you can just take a
moment to tell me a little

00:00:45.781 --> 00:00:46.911
